    "They covered various academic levels, varying from level three to level eight.",
    "The sample consisted of 256 students (n = 256) and 14 teachers (staff members) (n = 14).",
    "134 of the participant students are males, whereas 122 are females.",
    "Also, the teachers\" sample comprised 9 male and 5 female participants.",
    "As mentioned before, the students\" attitudinal perception of the impact of virtual learning on their engagement was tested by means of a questionnaire, whereas the teachers\" attitudes were tested by both a questionnaire and an interview."
